In these areas, the laws of Islam do not rule nor has the Islamic law produced indices of calculation to regulate legislations affecting life. It is a right granted to individuals and people to choose their behaviour. It is as valid and as sacred as freedom of movement, freedom of expression, freedom of profession, freedom of thought, honesty and justice those equal rights.”
